headline: Why Analysts Are Rethinking General Dynamics After Recent Results and Order Surge
summary: General Dynamics has seen its consensus analyst price target rise modestly, moving from $345.41 to $354.24 following its latest quarterly results. Analysts point to stronger order flow and resilient performance as key reasons for the upward adjustment. However, some caution remains regarding the ability to sustain growth across all segments.
